data.description: Next Generation/In-Law quarters with a separate entrance and fully equipped kitchen, ideal for accommodating the whole family. This 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom property, built in 2015. The first floor hosts a private 1-bedroom guest suite with separate laundry and a cozy living area for guests. The main living area is designed for gatherings and entertaining, while the second floor contains 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a laundry room for added convenience. Upgrades include hardwood floors throughout. The primary suite boasts a spacious walk-in closet and a luxurious en-suite bathroom. A prime location near shopping and schools, this home seamlessly combines style and functionality. The home is on a premium lot  with no neighbors behind you for added privacy.
